videos.description: Jessica Shepard gets the hoop and the harm, then the Lynx get the ball right back, and Shepard score through contact again.

videos.headline: Jessica Shepard notches two and-1 buckets in 8 seconds

videos.description: The Lynx take a two-point lead into the break thanks to a buzzer-beating 3 by Aerial Powers.

videos.description: The Lynx tie the score in the fourth quarter with some nice interior passing by Jessica Shepard to Sylvia Fowles.
